@startuml 06-seq-payment-webhook
title Sequence — Stripe Payment Webhook

participant Stripe
participant "Payment Service" as Payment
participant "Orders Service" as Orders
participant "Notifications Service" as Notif
database PostgreSQL
database Redis
participant SendGrid
participant "Notification Worker" as Worker

Stripe -> Payment: POST /payment/webhook\n(payment_intent.succeeded)
Payment -> Payment: Verify Stripe signature
Payment -> Orders: Confirm order (paymentIntentId)
Orders -> PostgreSQL: UPDATE order SET status = CONFIRMED
Orders -> Notif: Enqueue "order confirmed" email
Notif -> Redis: LPUSH email job
Payment --> Stripe: HTTP 200

Worker -> Redis: BRPOP email job
Worker -> SendGrid: POST /mail/send
SendGrid --> Worker: 202 Accepted
@enduml
